# Pages & Functionality

## Timer (page-timer)

The main study page.

Includes:

* Animated SVG countdown ring
* Mode selector with pill-style buttons
* Intent panel before each session:

  * Subject selection
  * Topic input
  * Goal setting
* Daily goal progress bar
* Virtual pet card with:

  * Energy bar
  * Happiness bar
  * XP bar
* Pet daily quests panel

### Main Functions

* `startTimer()`
* `pauseTimer()`
* `skipCycle()`
* `finishSession()`
* `updateTimerDisplay()`

---

## Dashboard (page-dashboard)

Features:

* 4 KPI cards:

  * Focus Hours
  * Sessions Completed
  * Focus Score
  * Current Streak
* Weekly bar chart displaying the last 7 days
* Weekly goal widget with completion indicators
* Motivational quote system with 10 rotating quotes and fade animation
* Monthly calendar heatmap with clickable day notes
* Exam schedule with countdown timers

### Tabs

* Today
* Week
* Month

These filter KPI values and delta badges accordingly.

---

## Subjects (page-subjects)

Features:

* Responsive card grid with auto-fill columns
* Each subject card includes:

  * Progress bar
  * Statistics
  * Rename button
  * Delete button
* Expandable detail drawer containing:

  * Notes
  * Session history
* Empty-state screen with call-to-action

---

## History (page-history)

Complete study session history with:

* Table view
* Card view
* Subject filtering
* Export functionality

---

## Analytics (page-piechart)

Five chart types:

1. Pie Chart
2. Daily Bar Chart
3. Cumulative Hours Trend
4. Hour Distribution
5. Focus Score Progression

---

## Achievements (page-achievements)

More than 40 achievements across categories:

* Sessions
* Study Hours
* Streaks
* Timer Modes
* Perfection
* Time of Day
* Subjects
* Levels

Achievements unlock with visual celebrations and XP rewards.

---

## Shop (page-shop)

Purchase:

* Achievement Frames
* Profile Badges

Using earned coins.

Includes a try-before-you-buy preview system so users can preview items before purchasing.

---

## Pet (page-pet)

Dedicated pet management page featuring:

* Detailed pet profile
* Pet milestones
* Rename functionality
* Active pet selection
* Pet shop for unlocking new pets

